OL,3,CCowboy builder victim 'let down' by
OL,4,CTrading Standards feels 'alone and
OL,5,Cangry'
OL,7,FIt's good news if you are a cowboy
OL,8,Fbuilder, or if you are selling illegal
OL,9,Fcigarettes, maybe some illicit vapes
OL,10,Fbeacuse there are now fewer people
OL,11,Fworking to stop you.
OL,13,FNew research suggests our defences
OL,14,Fagainst rogue traders have fallen so
OL,15,Flow that they have become "not fit for
OL,16,Fpurpose" with a reduction on criminal
OL,17,Fprosecutions and shop raids for
OL,18,Fsuspected illegal goods.
