OL,3,CCowboy builder victim 'let down' by
OL,4,CTrading Standards feels 'alone and
OL,5,Cangry'
OL,7,FClaire Dickenson says "I was let down
OL,8,Fby my builder - and then by Trading
OL,9,FStandards" as she now lives in a house
OL,10,Fthat shows all the signs of the
OL,11,Fstruggles she's been through fighting
OL,12,Fa builder for more than a year.
OL,14,FHer builder walked out after
OL,15,Fdisagreements over payments 13 months
OL,16,Fago, and now she and her family have
OL,17,Fbeen left living in a half-finished
OL,18,Fbuilding site without a kitchen.
OL,20,FShe says the contractor has left her
OL,21,Fout of pocket and out of options.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
