OL,7,F"We had a contract, we staged payments
OL,8,Fwe thought we were doing the right
OL,9,Fthing but when it actually came down
OL,10,Fto it, its very much a civil issue
OL,11,Fthat's difficult to support people on.
OL,13,F"In any other industry or issue with a
OL,14,Fproduct or service there is a backstop
OL,15,Fwith the consumer, with building work
OL,16,Fthere is seemingly nothing to protect
OL,17,Fthe consumer and that quite
OL,18,Ffrightening."
