OL,5,Cangry'
OL,7,FMs Dickenson says she is "panicked" at
OL,8,Fthe thought of paying to install a new
OL,9,Fkitchen and said she feels "alone,
OL,10,Fupset and quite angry that there is
OL,11,Fnothing to support consumers".
OL,13,FShe said Trading Standards do not have
OL,14,Fthe resources to help her get the
OL,15,Fmoney back she has lost and believes
OL,16,Fthis leaves an open door for any
OL,17,Ftrader that wants to abuse customers.
