OL,7,FTrading Standards officers work for
OL,8,Flocal councils enforcing consumer
OL,9,Frules. But there are fears that
OL,10,Fcutbacks have left some departments
OL,11,Fineffective.
OL,13,FFreedom of Information disclosures to
OL,14,FWhich? show 36 councils made no
OL,15,Fcriminal prosecutions in a whole year
OL,16,Fwhile 25 made only one prosecution of
OL,17,Frogue traders.
