OL,7,FConsumer expert Lisa Webb from Which?
OL,8,Fsaid: "Fewer than one in five of the
OL,9,FTrading Standards teams we spoke to
OL,10,Fhave not bought any form of criminal
OL,11,Finvestigation or prosecution in their
OL,12,Farea at all this year.
OL,14,F"That means that criminals effectively
OL,15,Fknow that they can get away with
OL,16,Fbreaking the law."
