OL,7,FTrading Standards has been cut by
OL,8,Faround 50% in the last 15 years
OL,9,Faccording to the sectors professional
OL,10,Fbody, Chartered Trading Standards
OL,11,FInstitute.
OL,13,FWe asked Ms Dickenson's local Trading
OL,14,FStandards for comment who told ITV
OL,15,FNews they understand her distress but
OL,16,Fthat they did not have a legal basis
OL,17,Fto take formal action.
