OL,7,FMeanwhile, it's not just the criminals
OL,8,Fwho benefit from the problems. Traders
OL,9,Fthat work hard to stick to the rules
OL,10,Fface unfair competition from rivals
OL,11,Fwho have no such scruples.
OL,13,FThere has often been a phrase to
OL,14,Fexplain police resourcing as "the thin
OL,15,Fblue line", for Trading Standards that
OL,16,Fline seems to be even more thin.
